{
 "name": "RPlog_Rendezvous_with_Karrde",
 "title": "Rendezvous with Karrde",
 "summary": "The fugitive group of Simon Sezirok, the Jedi Jessalyn Valios, the spacer Drew, and the mechanic Orson rendezvous with the smuggler chief Talon Karrde and his associate Lehec. Amid the careful maneuvering of those who live in the shadows, the band coordinates their next moves and the protection Karrde's organization can offer, the wary Simon and the principled Jessalyn navigating their tangled loyalties. The meeting weaves together the threads of trust, danger, and survival that bind the disparate group together under Karrde's shrewd influence.",
